    <title>Availability and requirements</title>
    <p>The current version of Systems Biology Simulation Core Library is available at the project’s homepage. The entire project, including source code and documentation, several versions of jar files containing only binaries, binaries together with source code, can be downloaded, optionally also as a version including all required third-party libraries.</p>
    <p><bold>Project name:</bold> Systems Biology Simulation Core Library</p>
